    <item>
      <title>爱立信达成协议，将美国公司出售给科赫集团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/ericsson-reaches-1-billion-deal-to-sell-us-firm-to-koch-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典电信设备制造商爱立信公司达成一项价值 10 亿美元的协议，将其美国呼叫路由业务 Iconectiv 出售给科赫公司的私人投资部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/ericsson-reaches-1-billion-deal-to-sell-us-firm-to-koch-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 03:44:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊付款延迟警告引起 Flex 司机恐慌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/amazon-s-payment-delay-warning-stirs-panic-among-flex-drivers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司警告使用自有车辆运送包裹的 Flex 司机，他们原定于周四收到的付款“可能会延迟”，这引起了习惯于在完成路线后立即付款的工人的恐慌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/amazon-s-payment-delay-warning-stirs-panic-among-flex-drivers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:40:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银在印度炙手可热的 IPO 市场中挑选股票赢家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/softbank-is-picking-stock-winners-in-india-s-red-hot-ipo-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度火爆的股票销售市场为日本科技投资者软银集团带来了收益，该公司自身的股价因令人失望的收益和人工智能的现实考验而受到打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/softbank-is-picking-stock-winners-in-india-s-red-hot-ipo-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 05:24:46 GMT</pubDate>
